{
  "stem": "16345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They only gave you 10,000 lire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we found a vendor-- I converted under a different name-- we found a vendor who was selling ice cream for 10,000 lire.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, I found out things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't convert every day of your life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- I went back to Germany, and then I decided I wanted to go home to Poland to see if anybody survived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because from Italy where else can you go?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you could go into-- into the ocean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I had no business in France, in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wouldn't would let me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the only place where they would let you in easily would be-- was into Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back to Germany, and then I hopped-- I found out which trains were going in my direction, which is Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I hopped a train that had all kinds of factory equipment that the Russians were taking back from Germany to Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got off in-- in Poland someplace, and then I hopped another train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it's curious that at the time I had acquired, through one way or another, civilian clothes, and my hair had grown up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, through all this time, my-- I had been-- I had a-- a sort of a really bald haircut, and my hair had started growing back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I came to Poland, I-- we found-- I found a place where they were givi-- where they would give you a meal, but I didn't know if they would give meals to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [SIGH] I became a non-Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what's your name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I gave him some kind of a Polish-sounding name, and I got a meal.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
